
MVD-tool

** Info

A simple C++ parser and tool for the MVD3 neuroscience file format

- provide a tool to convert MVD2 to MVD3
- provide a tool to export MVD to CSV
- provide a simple header base parser for MVD2
- provide a parser based on the HighFive library for MVD3


** compilation

# MVDTool has three main dependencies
 * boost 
 * HDF5
 * HighFive (https://github.com/BlueBrain/HighFive )


# configure, compile
mkdir build; pushd build
cmake ../
make

# install
make install


** Python API example 
# get all the position for all the neuron in a circuit 

import mvdtool as mvd
f = mvd.MVD3.File("tests/circuit.mvd3")
p = f.getPositions()
print(p)

# list all the properties available in a circuit file

import mvdtool as mvd
f = mvd.MVD3.File("tests/circuit.mvd3")
dir(f)

# list all the morphologies used by every neuron

import mvdtool as mvd
f = mvd.MVD3.File("tests/circuit.mvd3")
m = f.getMorphologies()
print(m)









